{"tid":1960912,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 係屋企都做到既簡單飲品","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T07:36:42.000Z","uid":304230,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d1826ab4d2df85e78c83fc96997498b3d7465e38","tid":1960912,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"教大家係屋企都整到既簡單mocktail<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfHxDN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfHxDN3.jpg&h=a0cd4dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料<br />\nRaspberry 5粒<br />\nHoney 2 Spoon<br />\n薄荷葉 幾塊<br />\n檸檬 1/8個<br />\n茶 250ml (津路都可以)<br />\n<br />\n做法<br />\n加raspberry 薄荷葉 mudmud佢<br />\n加honey加茶加冰shakeshake佢<br />\n吱d檸檬汁係面 搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪好簡單呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩味想飲既可以留個comment <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡量會諗d屋企都整到既比大家試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識up影片 可以去我地ig睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teaonlyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fteaonlyhk%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=c0f3ba32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/teaonlyhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n會係屋企整既整完post黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66ab2825ff2141b2a1537b99ac8183e95d64a65","tid":1960912,"uid":26726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03ee8e4804bfb1ba1d57c514281336c78e93364","tid":1960912,"uid":269202,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:24:15.000Z","msg"